Simulation Results (LTA Estimates)

Usage

data(results_lta_est)

Format

A dataframe with 486 rows and 20 columns:

taskid

Task ID.

replications

Number of replications.

parnames

Parameter names

parameter

Population parameter value.

model

Fitted model.

separation

Level of separation.

n

Sample size.

est

Mean parameter estimate.

se

Mean standard error.

z

Mean \(z\) statistic.

p

Mean \(p\)-value.

ll

Mean lower limit of the 95% confidence interval.

ul

Mean upper limit of the 95% confidence interval.

sig

Proportion of statistically significant results.

theta_hit

Proportion of replications where the confidence intervals contained the population parameter.

sq_error

Mean squared error.

se_bias

Bias in standard error estimate.

coverage

Coverage probability.

power

Statistical power.

bias

Bias.
